      "title": "Ranil takes oath as the eighth executive president",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe was sworn in as the eighth Executive President a little while ago at the Parliament complex. Before the Chief Justice, the President took his oath. Defense chiefs including the commanders of the three armed forces joined the occasion."
      ],
